summary:
With more than 21 years in field of management and leadership, proven ability to build up and develop sustainable business operations, with strong focus on delivering results in the Healthcare Business. 
With profound experience in leading promotional and commercial sales and key account management, as well as HR development, empowered stakeholders to create value. 
Strategic and also hands-on!
